# Per-language ignores live in their own subtree (appunvs/ios, appunvs/android,
# runtime/, relay/, etc.).  This top-level file only catches scratch directories
# that tooling drops at the repo root.

# Worktrees created by background subagents.  These are local-only — the
# corresponding work is delivered via PRs from the agent's own branches.
.claude/worktrees/
